  "body": "🎯 What: The Google Client ID was hardcoded in the frontend code.\n⚠️ Risk: Hardcoding sensitive or environment-specific values in source code makes it difficult to manage configurations across different environments (e.g., staging vs production) and poses a security risk if the codebase is exposed.\n🛡️ Solution: Moved the Client ID to an environment variable (`VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID`). Added appropriate error handling and fallback UI in case the environment variable is not provided.\n\n---\n*PR created automatically by Jules for task [2902249539694649287](https://jules.google.com/task/2902249539694649287) started by @pietromauri*",
